I have just now posted the latest source code for Cantera at the 
sourceforge site (cantera-1.5.3-src.zip), along with a document 
describing how to build everything from the source code under Windows.  
This version builds successfully on Windows, linux, and Mac OS X. A 
corresponding binary distribution for Windows will be posted soon.
